      <hedline>
        <hl1>Practicing Compassion</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Art Vanden Houten letter holds compassion is integral to being doctor; drawing</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>For too long, we have viewed compassion in physicians as a welcome extra. Medicine can only truly rise to the honored calling it is when we recognize that compassion is integral to being a doctor and practicing the craft of medicine.</p>
        <p>ART VANDEN HOUTEN  St. Augustine, Fla.</p>
      </block>
